lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps and Katie Ledecky will both feature in the United States 4 x 100 meters freestyle relay teams at the Rio Olympics, USA Today reported on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Phelps, Ledecky Set for 4x100 Relays : Report
